Three Months Return & Three Months Volatility Rolling
In [118]:
sp500_mth_return.reset_index(level=0, inplace=True)
monthly_date=sp500_mth_return["Date"].reset_index().drop(columns=["index"])
In [119]:
sp500_3mths_return_rolling=sp500_mth_return.rolling(3).sum().merge(monthly_date, on=
                                             monthly_date.index).drop(columns=["key_0"]).set_index(["Date"]) * (252 ** 0.5) / (60 ** 0.5)
vix_3mths_volatility_rolling=vix_mth_volatility.rolling(3).sum().merge(monthly_date, on=
                                             monthly_date.index).drop(columns=["key_0"]).set_index(["Date"])
